                            <comment id="17620279" author="smiklosovic" created="Wed, 19 Oct 2022 11:53:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems to me that this problem exists across all versions we support, .build/build-rat.xml is same everywhere&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17620294" author="smiklosovic" created="Wed, 19 Oct 2022 12:02:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch for 3.0 is here, &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/1926&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/1926&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
build is in progress here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/2022/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/2022/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17620310" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 19 Oct 2022 12:15:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;/cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mck&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mck&quot;&gt;mck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17620362" author="smiklosovic" created="Wed, 19 Oct 2022 13:33:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We agreed offline with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mck&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mck&quot;&gt;mck&lt;/a&gt; that this is not a blocker for releases we are trying to ship right now so the current voting is still in progress. I will finish all builds for all branches and we might just merge it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17620846" author="michaelsembwever" created="Thu, 20 Oct 2022 07:28:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17621083" author="smiklosovic" created="Thu, 20 Oct 2022 12:37:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;3.0 &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/2028/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/2028/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17621121" author="smiklosovic" created="Thu, 20 Oct 2022 13:50:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have tested it manually for all other branches. I consider that to be actually better than CI as we currently can not mimic what happens when git executable is not present.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17622112" author="smiklosovic" created="Fri, 21 Oct 2022 08:24:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I will fix &quot;Fix Version/s&quot; when we have tags for new yet-unreleased versions and the deal here is that this wont go to 3.0.28 and similar yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
